And there’s 4 main ones: “philia” which is the love you feel for your true friends; “eros” which is the love felt in sexual passion; “storge” which is the love of unconditional empathy as you might feel for your family or your favorite sports team where no matter what happens you stick with them; and “agape” which is the strongest of all - the pure unstoppable love that can only be compared to the love god feels for his creation, which parents also feel for their children and spouses feel for each other.
